    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS SPICER AUTOMATE-2 - REMOVE - LOWER SHIFT TOWER (FIGURE 3)</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>LOWER SHIFT TOWER (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1302203">FIGURE 3</hotlnk>)
        </title>
        <figure id="f1302203" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302203" filename="../figg13/G1302203.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 3. Lower Shift Tower</caption>
        </figure>
        <specpara>
            <warning>
                <para>Shut off and bleed the air system to prevent lines from whipping.</para>
            </warning>
        </specpara>
        <para>Remove the upper shift tower assembly. Remove the lower shift tower assembly from the unit and out of the
            vehicle (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1302204">Figure 4</hotlnk>). Check the housing for cracks and other damage. Replace if
            necessary.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1302204" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302204" filename="../figg13/G1302204.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 4. Shift Tower Assembly</caption>
